Revision history for Devel-IntelliPerl

0.02    2009-06-16
        - Added Editor::Vim (thanks to M. Grimes)
        - fixed infinite loop regarding update_inc (M. Grimes)
        - works now with untitled documents
        - changed TextMate script to redirect errors and warnings to /dev/null
        - fancy context menu for choosing a method
        - Removed Text::Table dependency (fixes failing tests)
        - support for Types in Moose attributes
        - support for MooseX::Method::Signatures' "returns" keyword
        - Support for Union Types
        

0.01    2009-06-12
        - First version, released on an unsuspecting world.

